// Description
// Converts a value to the word data type.
// Syntax
// word(x)
// word(h, l)
// (word)x (C-style type conversion)
// Parameters
// x: a value. Allowed data types: any type.
// h: the high-order (leftmost) byte of the word.
// l: the low-order (rightmost) byte of the word.
// Returns
// Data type: word.